## ⚡ Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Install globally
npm install -g git+https://github.com/<your-repo>/geminiopenv-ai.git

# 2. Set your API key (just one required!)
# Windows CMD:
setx GEMINI_API_KEY "your_key_here"
# Windows PowerShell:
[System.Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable("GEMINI_API_KEY","your_key_here","User")
# macOS / Linux:
echo 'export GEMINI_API_KEY="your_key_here"' >> ~/.bashrc && source ~/.bashrc

# 3. Launch
geminiviratpro
```

That's it. You're ready. 🚀

