## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| 🤖 **Dual AI Engine** | Gemini as primary, OpenRouter as automatic fallback |
| 🧠 **Autonomous Agent** | Breaks complex tasks into steps, executes tools, iterates to completion |
| 📁 **File Operations** | Read, write, list, search, and visualize file trees |
| 🐍 **Code Execution** | Run Python code safely with timeout protection |
| 🎨 **Image Generation** | Generate images from text prompts directly in terminal |
| 💾 **Conversation Memory** | Sliding window of 50 messages with full context recall |
| 🌊 **Streaming Responses** | Real-time token-by-token output |
| 🌍 **Cross-Platform** | Works on Windows, macOS, and Linux |

