## 🏗 Architecture

```
geminiviratpro (npm global command)
    │
    ▼
 index.js (Node.js launcher)
    │
    ▼
 main.py (CLI interface & command router)
    │
    ├── router.py ──► ai_gemini.py (Primary)
    │               └► ai_openrouter.py (Fallback)
    │
    ├── agent.py (Autonomous task execution)
    │
    ├── memory.py (Conversation context)
    │
    ├── image_gen.py (Image generation)
    │
    └── tools/
        ├── file_ops.py (File system operations)
        └── code_runner.py (Safe code execution)
```

