## 📦 Installation

### Prerequisites

- **Node.js** 14+ and **npm**
- **Python** 3.8+
- **pip package:** `requests` (`pip install requests`)

### Install from GitHub

```bash
npm install -g git+https://github.com/<your-username>/geminiopenv-ai.git
```

### Install from Local Clone

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/geminiopenv-ai.git
cd geminiopenv-ai
npm install -g .
```

### Verify Installation

```bash
geminiviratpro
```

You should see:

```
╔══════════════════════════════════════════╗
║        🔥 Gemini Virat Pro AI           ║
║     Your Hybrid AI Terminal Assistant    ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════╝

  Gemini     ● Connected
  OpenRouter ● Connected
```

