## 📖 Commands Reference

| Command | Description | Example |
|---------|-------------|---------|
| `/chat <message>` | Chat with AI | `/chat explain Python decorators` |
| `/code <task>` | Generate or explain code | `/code write a FastAPI server` |
| `/agent <task>` | Autonomous multi-step task | `/agent create a Flask todo app` |
| `/image <prompt>` | Generate an image | `/image a futuristic city at sunset` |
| `/files` | List files in current directory | `/files` |
| `/memory` | Show conversation history | `/memory` |
| `/exit` | Exit the CLI | `/exit` |

### Usage Examples

```
🔥 Gemini Virat Pro AI > /chat What is the difference between REST and GraphQL?

🔥 Gemini Virat Pro AI > /code write a binary search in Rust

🔥 Gemini Virat Pro AI > /agent create a Python web scraper that extracts headlines from Hacker News

🔥 Gemini Virat Pro AI > /image a cyberpunk hacker cat wearing sunglasses
```

