## ⚙️ Configuration

All configuration lives in `config.py`:

```python
GEMINI_MODEL    = "gemini-2.0-flash"       # Primary model
OPENROUTER_MODEL = "google/gemini-2.0-flash-exp:free"  # Fallback
MAX_AGENT_ITERATIONS = 10                  # Agent loop limit
MEMORY_SIZE     = 50                       # Messages to remember
CODE_TIMEOUT    = 30                       # Seconds before code kill
```

